#. <section class="sutta" id="sn45.26"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn45.26:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 45"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 45"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn45.26:0.2"
msgid "3. Micchattavagga"
msgstr "3. The Wrong Way"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn45.26:0.3"
msgid "26. Dutiyaasappurisasutta"
msgstr "26. A Good Person (2nd)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn45.26:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn45.26:1.2"
msgid ""
"“Asappurisañca vo, bhikkhave, desessāmi, asappurisena asappurisatarañca."
msgstr "“Mendicants, I will teach you a bad person and a worse person,"

msgctxt "sn45.26:1.3"
msgid "Sappurisañca vo, bhikkhave, desessāmi sappurisena sappurisatarañca."
msgstr "a good person and a better person."

msgctxt "sn45.26:1.4"
msgid "Taṃ suṇātha."
msgstr "Listen …"

msgctxt "sn45.26:1.5"
msgid "Katamo ca, bhikkhave, asappuriso?"
msgstr "And what is a bad person?"

msgctxt "sn45.26:1.6"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco micchādiṭṭhiko hoti … pe … micchāsamādhi—"
msgstr ""
"It’s someone who has wrong view, wrong thought, wrong speech, wrong action, "
"wrong livelihood, wrong effort, wrong mindfulness, and wrong immersion."

msgctxt "sn45.26:1.7"
msgid "ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, asappuriso."
msgstr "This is called a bad person."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn45.26:2.1"
msgid "Katamo ca, bhikkhave, asappurisena asappurisataro?"
msgstr "And what is a worse person?"

msgctxt "sn45.26:2.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco micchādiṭṭhiko hoti … pe … micchāsamādhi, "
"micchāñāṇī, micchāvimutti—"
msgstr ""
"It’s someone who has wrong view, wrong thought, wrong speech, wrong action, "
"wrong livelihood, wrong effort, wrong mindfulness, wrong immersion, wrong "
"knowledge, and wrong freedom."

msgctxt "sn45.26:2.3"
msgid "ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, asappurisena asappurisataro."
msgstr "This is called a worse person."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn45.26:3.1"
msgid "Katamo ca, bhikkhave, sappuriso?"
msgstr "And what is a good person?"

msgctxt "sn45.26:3.2"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco sammādiṭṭhiko hoti … pe … sammāsamādhi—"
msgstr ""
"It’s someone who has right view, right thought, right speech, right action, "
"right livelihood, right effort, right mindfulness, and right immersion."

msgctxt "sn45.26:3.3"
msgid "ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, sappuriso."
msgstr "This is called a good person."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "sn45.26:4.1"
msgid "Katamo ca, bhikkhave, sappurisena sappurisataro?"
msgstr "And what is a better person?"

msgctxt "sn45.26:4.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco sammādiṭṭhiko hoti … pe … sammāsamādhi, sammāñāṇī, "
"sammāvimutti—"
msgstr ""
"It’s someone who has right view, right thought, right speech, right action, "
"right livelihood, right effort, right mindfulness, right immersion, right "
"knowledge, and right freedom."

msgctxt "sn45.26:4.3"
msgid "ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, sappurisena sappurisataro”ti."
msgstr "This is called a better person.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn45.26:4.4"
msgid "Chaṭṭhaṃ."
msgstr ""
